fehd.ADR_TC: 南丫島索罟灣模達灣7號7約485地段

reviews.text: Good beach restaurant, somebodies likes to raise the marriage banquet at here during evening.  Provide some water activities facilities rent during summer hot season.
Great place. Great fun too.
Island romance

We had a good experience at the bay near the Mo Tat Wan pier on Lamma Island. We both ordered Fish & Chips and it was lovely. With a beer and water reasonable price 260 HKD. Since it is the only restaurant at Mo Tat Wan I think we will go here more often 😀

NOT RECOMMENDED, the experience was a disaster, the owner was arrogant, rude, and she knows you have no alternative choice nearby. Ruined my special occasion with my girlfriend. Despite the extremely poor service, food was mediocre, and the beach was small, and full of garbage. If you need a restaurant nearby the beach with a relaxing ambiance. I would rather recommend the Discovery Bay.
